---
// ServicesSection - What we deliver for gym owners
---

<section class="services-section" id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="header-content">
        <span class="label">What We Deliver</span>
        <h2>Everything You Need to Scale.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="header-description">A complete growth system designed specifically for premium fitness facilities. No generic templates. No cookie-cutter approaches.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- Service 1 -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Precision Lead Generation</h3>
        <p>Meta and Google ad campaigns engineered to attract high-ticket prospects who are ready to invest in their fitness journey - not tire-kickers.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Custom audience targeting</li>
          <li>High-converting ad creative</li>
          <li>Landing page optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 2 -->
      <div class="service-card featured">
        <div class="service-badge">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sales System Implementation</h3>
        <p>We build and install a complete sales infrastructure so your team can convert leads into members consistently, without being "salesy".</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>CRM setup and automation</li>
          <li>Consultation scripts</li>
          <li>Staff training sessions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 3 -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/>
            <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Retention & LTV Systems</h3>
        <p>Automated onboarding sequences, engagement campaigns, and loyalty programs that turn one-time members into lifelong advocates.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Onboarding automation</li>
          <li>Engagement sequences</li>
          <li>Churn prevention alerts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="section-cta">
      <p>Not sure which service is right for you?</p>
      <a href="#booking" class="btn btn-outline">
        Let's Talk Strategy
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: hsl(var(--cream));
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .services-section {
      padding: 8rem 0;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: hsl(var(--forest) / 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .header-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Services Grid */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .service-card {
    position: relative;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--forest) / 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: hsl(var(--forest) / 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px hsl(var(--forest) / 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    background: hsl(var(--forest));
    color: white;
    border-color: hsl(var(--forest));
  }

  .service-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.75rem;
    left: 2rem;
    background: hsl(var(--gold));
    color: hsl(var(--forest));
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-icon {
    width: 3.5rem;
    height: 3.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: hsl(var(--forest));
  }

  .service-card.featured .service-icon {
    color: hsl(var(--gold));
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-card.featured p {
    color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.7);
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.6);
  }

  .service-card.featured .service-features li {
    color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.6);
  }

  .service-features li::before {
    content: "";
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: hsl(var(--gold));
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Section CTA */
  .section-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .section-cta {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  .section-cta p {
    color: hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.6);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: hsl(var(--forest));
    border: 2px solid hsl(var(--forest));
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: hsl(var(--forest));
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-outline svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
